股先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過騰訊係both<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩樣都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你唔想打太多字<br />\n揀一樣講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff853377d9ff96b4bd66d7cc706977f7d645d9d","tid":246594,"uid":107720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:36:07.000Z","msg":"5月17日，騰訊控股（00700 ) 今天公佈截至2017年4月30日未經審核的第一季度綜合業績。總收入495.52億，同比增長55%超預期！<br />\n<br />\n一季度經營盈利為人民幣192.72億元（27.93億美元），同比增長44%，略超預期。<br />\n<br />\n一季度經營利潤率由去年同期的42%降至39%。<br />\n<br />\n一季度每股基本盈利為人民幣1.540元，每股攤薄盈利為人民幣1.522元。<br />\n<br />\n微信和WeChat的合併月活躍賬戶數達到9.38億，同比增長23%。"},{"pid":"12914212b2d2abf50119ccc7a0409899210072b6","tid":246594,"uid":47099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.futunn.com/market/38070?src=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.futunn.com%2Fmarket%2F38070%3Fsrc%3D0&d=BSPHu9UqRwj8n7oVkU4q%2Bcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=61058c3b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.futunn.com/market/38070?src=0</a><br />\n殘體<br />\n<br />\n5月17日，腾讯控股（00700 ) 今天公布截至2017年4月30日未经审核的第一季度综合业绩。总收入495.52亿，同比增长55%超预期！<br />\n<br />\n一季度经营盈利为人民币192.72亿元（27.93亿美元），同比增长44%，略超预期。<br />\n<br />\n经营利润率由去年同期的42%降至39%。<br />\n<br />\n本公司权益持有人应占盈利144.76亿元（20.98亿美元），同比增长58%。<br />\n<br />\n每股基本盈利1.540元，每股摊薄盈利1.522元。<br />\n<br />\n网络游戏收入增长34%至228.11亿元，主要反映来自智能手机游戏（如《王者荣耀》及《龙之谷》）及PC客户端游戏（如《英雄联盟》及《地下城与勇士》）收入的增长。<br />\n<br />\n微信和WeChat的合并月活跃账户数达到9.38亿，同比增长23%。"},{"pid":"1d044aea96c05b7e55c261e81e27aaa60ea181a1","tid":246594,"uid":72825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:38:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5月17日，騰訊控股（00700 ) 今天公佈截至2017年4月30日未經審核的第一季度綜合業績。總收入495.52億，同比增長55%超預期！<br />\n<br />\n一季度經營盈利為人民幣192.72億元（27.93億美元），同比增長44%，略超預期。<br />\n<br />\n一季度經營利潤率由去年同期的42%降至39%。<br />\n<br />\n一季度每股基本盈利為人民幣1.540元，每股攤薄盈利為人民幣1.522元。<br />\n<br />\n微信和WeChat的合併月活躍賬戶數達到9.38億，同比增長23%。</blockquote><br />\n今次仲唔發"},{"pid":"263e137794fdb94a8f7c3dd3206719999ecb59d9","tid":246594,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:44:47.000Z","msg":"700 go go go"},{"pid":"7fd4949cfad2a1c3ec88cf8ab587fd3cd3665ccb","tid":246594,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:46:39.000Z","msg":"你係股東會OPENRICE黎<br />\n<br />\n勁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a762d9de0e1cd6fc299bd843f4c686bf8fba5697","tid":246594,"uid":9844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:47:46.000Z","msg":"盈利增長5x% 勁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667006c7cb52ea65f206806abc494a296e84a7cf","tid":246594,"uid":34621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:49:25.000Z","msg":"This time fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b914854eb4c594415a60a4ac85b37ab7bbfba10e","tid":246594,"uid":107720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:50:36.000Z","msg":"終於搵到兩餐晏仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2133ba914ff4cca8105681e3f28126f78a3fc8dc","tid":246594,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:52:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盈利增長5x% 勁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收入"},{"pid":"98d4bdc482ed9a33bb60651b340c1e3ba2f8083e","tid":246594,"uid":9844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>盈利增長5x% 勁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br 