（ｊｎ）"},{"pid":"c3334e9f2ee8ac8dfff04c89976641f515d20c8e","tid":246594,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T09:09:11.000Z","msg":"股王無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6e2fc073828c73efaa36ff997e80e23312eb8b","tid":246594,"uid":54884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T09:22:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每股攤薄盈利為人民幣1.522元<br />\n<br />\n股東出HK$ 259.80, 先賺1.522元人仔？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n1季"},{"pid":"52bce020e42d77152ca694f0bddd3321322cdcfb","tid":246594,"uid":34621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T09:22:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每股攤薄盈利為人民幣1.522元<br />\n<br />\n股東出HK$ 259.80, 先賺1.522元人仔？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每季啊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nX 4 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36d2a89799b7bcae1ed8c679d34f6e3d3dd7222","tid":246594,"uid":107720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每股攤薄盈利為人民幣1.522元<br />\n<br />\n股東出HK$ 259.80, 先賺1.522元人仔？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" clas